signature.instructions:
Extract structured data from the document image.

Extract the following fields from the document:
- Before-Tax Total (currency) (required): Subtotal before taxes are applied
  • Look for 'Subtotal' label
  • Usually appears before tax line
- After-Tax Total (currency) (required): Final total including all taxes
  • Look for 'Total', 'Amount', or 'Balance' label
  • Usually at the bottom of receipt

Return values in a structured format. Be precise and extract exact values from the document.

fields.description: Document image to extract data from
